&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Analytic Services Inc. (ANSER) is seeking a Contingency Force Protection Planner to help optimizing operations that span the entire enterprise of an organization. In this Contingency Force Protection role, you will help provide oversight and advocacy for Military Police capability requirements in the Fleet Marine Force to achieve impact and value from their investments in both people and technology.&lt;/p&gt;
