&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Will be responsible for coordination with service Headquarters for the provision of Military Police Operations input into policy and service assessment (e.g. IGMC)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the development, evaluation, and implementation of standard operating procedures (SOPs) that support requirements for Detainee Operations, Identity Operations, Joint Security Operations, and INDOPACOM Homeland Defense Operations and system security plans to protect and defend personnel, critical infrastructure, processes and critical asset protection for assigned and gained forces&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop Mission Assurance, Force Protection and security briefings and guidance as required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the development, coordination, and monitoring of security programs, including reviewing and approving documentation, conducting site surveys, and&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage activities related to protection of MARFORPAC, INDOPACOM and gained units as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
