&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in data analysis or data science, ideally in support of government, defense, or intelligence programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in data analysis and visualization tools such as Python, R, SQL, Tableau, or Power BI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with large and complex datasets from multiple sources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving skills and the ability to communicate complex information clearly and concisely.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of statistical methods, machine learning techniques, or data modeling frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage multiple priorities in a fast-paced, mission-focused environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active security clearance or the ability to obtain one may be required depending on the position.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience and knowledge of defense agencies and their technology policies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
